name: Layer 2 Decentraland High Tops
description: Meta Mike, Innovation Lead at VERSED, has designed a custom Decentraland Wearable for Polygon protocol hodlers and enthusiasts. Built with metaverse interoperability in mind, these 'Layer 2' high tops emphasize both style and utility. This 1 of 10 drip drop is the first DCL wearable produced by VERSED, and our goal is to make these available to owners across as many virtual worlds as possible. Wear these shoes in Decentraland!
